 on either port causes `log.Fatalf` to terminate the whole process. Because the metrics server runs in a background goroutine, a runtime error from it will also kill the process via `log.Fatalf`. There is no partial-failure or graceful-shutdown path.\n","structuredPatch":[],"originalFile":null}}
